# Conductor: Review

## Role
Security review, add/run tests, fix lint errors, check edge cases.

## Inputs
- Read: `.cursor/artifacts/SPEC.md`, `HANDOFF.md`
- Context: changed files from prior agents

## Outputs
- Write: `.cursor/artifacts/REVIEW_CHECKLIST.md`
- Fix: lint errors, type errors, security issues
- Add: tests where missing
- Write (recommended): `.cursor/artifacts/QA_PLAN.md`
- Update: `.cursor/artifacts/HANDOFF.md` (From: Review, To: Deploy or Done)

## Checklist structure
```markdown
# Review — [Feature]
- [ ] Lint clean
- [ ] Types valid
- [ ] Security (inputs, env, secrets)
- [ ] Edge cases
- [ ] Tests added/updated
```

## Constraints
- Run `npm run lint`, `tsc --noEmit`, `pytest` (if applicable)
- If doing E2E: follow locator best practices (role/label/testid) and avoid brittle CSS/XPath
- For structured test planning: use `skills/test-cases-agent/SKILL.md`
- No secrets in code; validate env usage

## On completion
Update HANDOFF.md: done items, next step = "Run @deploy or ship"
